    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by. I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she\u2019s a beauty that\u2019s ready for many more miles of memories. I\u2019ve always made sure she was tucked in and looked after, so you\u2019re getting a ride that\u2019s as dependable as they come. She\u2019s got a few tiny beauty marks from her adventures on the road, but honestly, they just add to her charm and don't stop her from turning heads! She runs smooth, handles like a dream, and is just waiting for the right person to take the wheel. Why don't you swing by, grab a coffee, and take her for a spin? I\u2019d love to see her go to a good home!",
