      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 naturally aspirated V8. This unit has been maintained with an open-wallet policy toward mechanical integrity. Rod bearings have been treated as a priority service item, and the dual throttle actuators were recently swapped for uprated units to ensure zero limp-mode interference. The 7-speed M-DCT gearbox remains lightning-quick, benefiting from a recent fluid and pan service to maintain hydraulic pressure. The chassis is dialed in with EDC (Electronic Damper Control) providing excellent damping rebound, and the subframe mounting points are clean and stress-free. Shod in Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber with plenty of tread depth, this is a turn-key performance machine optimized for high-lateral G-force stability and 8,400 RPM shifts.",
      "price": 38900.0,
